{"tid":531648,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"被指網店出現漏洞，OnePlus 暫停接受信用卡付款","createTime":"2018-01-17T04:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T01:00:48.000Z","uid":20738,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d49599ade3476acbfccba3cde792ccac4546e0c6","tid":531648,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:56:45.000Z","msg":"劉明睇打手又出「臭蟲論」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/01/16/oneplus-halts-credit-card-payments-fraud/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2Foneplus-halts-credit-card-payments-fraud%2F&d=W5fWDhjqhJPaoiRY8dxCENZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a0042703\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/01/16/oneplus-halts-credit-card-payments-fraud/</a><br />\n<br />\n被指網店出現漏洞，OnePlus 暫停接受信用卡付款<br />\n<br />\n有不少人以信用卡購物後，後來都發現有未授權交易。<br />\n<br />\n最近有不少人都表示他們在一加手機的官方網店 <a href=\"http://OnePlus.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOnePlus.net&d=W5fWDhjqhJPaoiRY8dxCENZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=fe74a583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">OnePlus.net</a> 以信用卡購物後，發現帳單上出現莫名的未授權交易。OnePlus 今天發出新聞稿，指他們正調查事件，並暫停接受以信用卡作為付費方式。現在想要在 <a href=\"http://OnePlus.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOnePlus.net&d=W5fWDhjqhJPaoiRY8dxCENZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=fe74a583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">OnePlus.net</a> 購物的話就只可以使用 PayPal 付款，同時一加會嘗試尋求其他安全的支付方式。<br />\n<br />\n在此呼籲各位讀者朋友，如果你曾經有在 <a href=\"http://OnePlus.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOnePlus.net&d=W5fWDhjqhJPaoiRY8dxCENZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=fe74a583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">OnePlus.net</a> 以信用卡購物的話，記緊留意帳單上有沒有出現未授權的項目。如有發現，請盡快聯絡銀行或發卡機構尋求協助，避免進一步的損失。"},{"pid":"d958f467f400aafca400f4315cf8fc1682135a62","tid":531648,"uid":20738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"藉口都幫你地諗埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔關部手機事，網站嘅問題」"},{"pid":"c3cdc4d43d